# Unified Course Configuration + Pricing Panel

## Problem

The system has **two disconnected course systems**:

| System | Source | Used By |
|---|---|---|
| [Program](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/components/admin/AcademicManager.tsx#11-18) model | [Academic.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/Academic.ts) (DB) | Registration, eligibility, batches — but **no admin CRUD UI** |
| [courseData.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/data/courseData.ts) | Hardcoded file (22 courses, 551 lines) | Public website course listing — **not editable** |
| [CoursePricing](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/CoursePricing.ts#3-15) model | DB | Pricing overlay on website — separate admin page (link exists but **page is missing**) |

> [!CAUTION]
> Courses on the website are completely hardcoded. Any course change requires a code deployment. The [Program](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/components/admin/AcademicManager.tsx#11-18) model (used for student registration) and `courseData` (used for website display) are **not linked at all**.

## Proposed Solution

Extend the **[Program](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/components/admin/AcademicManager.tsx#11-18) model** with website display fields + embedded pricing → single source of truth. Delete the hardcoded [courseData.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/data/courseData.ts) and [CoursePricing](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/CoursePricing.ts#3-15) model.

## Proposed Changes

### Model: Extend [IProgram](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/Academic.ts#5-14) in [Academic.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/Academic.ts)

Add website display + pricing fields to the existing [Program](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/components/admin/AcademicManager.tsx#11-18) schema:

```diff
// New fields on Program
+ shortDescription: string        // public website
+ image: string                   // course image URL
+ eligibilitySummary: string      // e.g. "12th Pass"
+ syllabus: string[]              // topic list
+ careerOptions: string[]         // career paths
+ pricing: {
+     totalFee: number
+     paymentType: 'one-time' | 'semester-wise' | 'installments'
+     offerPrice: number | null
+     isOfferActive: boolean
+     offerValidUntil: Date | null
+     offerLabel: string
+     seatLimit: number | null
+     currency: string             // default 'INR'
+     scholarshipAvailable: boolean
+ }
+ displayOrder: number             // sort order on website
```

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The existing `is_active` field on Program will serve as the **Active/Inactive toggle** — inactive courses won't appear on the website or in registration.

---

### API Changes

#### [MODIFY] `/api/admin/academic` (existing)
Already manages Programs via the [AcademicManager.tsx](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/components/admin/AcademicManager.tsx) component. We'll add a **new dedicated route** instead to avoid breaking existing academic config.

#### [NEW] `/api/admin/courses/route.ts`
- **GET** — list all programs with pricing, student counts, sorted by displayOrder
- **POST** — create new course (program + pricing + website fields)
- **PATCH** — update any course field (including pricing, status toggle)

#### [NEW] `/api/admin/courses/[id]/route.ts`
- **PATCH** — update single course
- **DELETE** — soft-disable (set `is_active = false`), with check: if students linked, block hard delete

#### [MODIFY] [/api/public/course-pricing/route.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/public/course-pricing/route.ts)
Update to read from Program's embedded pricing instead of separate CoursePricing model.

#### [NEW] `/api/public/courses/route.ts`
Replace hardcoded courseData. Returns active programs with website fields + computed pricing.

