## Migration Strategy

1. Add new fields to Program model (backward compatible, all optional with defaults)
2. Create a one-time migration script to seed existing `courseData` entries into Program documents and copy [CoursePricing](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/CoursePricing.ts#3-15) data into embedded fields
3. Update APIs and UI
4. Remove old files

> [!WARNING]
> The migration script should be run once to copy the 22 hardcoded courses + any existing pricing data into the Program collection. Existing students' `programId` references won't break since we're extending, not replacing.

